{"type": "article", "id": 5774, "title": "Axor STARCK V 水龙头", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-02T07:40:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233944C0UKS4qGWfbYysAi.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是法国设计师 Philippe Starck 为德国著名卫浴品牌 Axor 设计的水龙头 STARCK V，设计师的设计灵感源自 Klaus Grohe 对水的涡旋现象的探索，赋予其雕塑一般的造型，简单又清爽，独特的透明设计与螺旋上升式的出水方式也非常罕见，使得用户可以直观地看到水从水管流出的瞬间。\r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODg0MzI5ODYw\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233943P7QoH3fDFIUZ0VXp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233943XaVrJGBy4igvk9Pm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}